pageContext.claim: “[Pelosi] said no, no, shifty Schiff told the truth when he said that. Stephanopoulos said no, wait a minute, no, it wasn't the truth. It was a falsehood. No, no, it's the truth. pageContext.analysis: Trump appears to be referring to an Oct. 4 interview on ABC News. However, this conversation is not represented in the transcript.
